body_html:
I spent much time debugging this issue in my own code and googling found this (NiHaoUCAS, this will possibly help you as well):
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/42513613/tensorflow-dynamic-rnn-regressor-valueerror-dimension-mismatch

Further search in the github repository found this issue. It's obviously a pain point for users.
Edit: note that one of the Google Brain developers answered in SO that it is a bug in one of the execution branches and that they are working on fixing it.
